My dearest Mary,

762
01:13:40,018 --> 01:13:43,215
by the time you read this,
I will be on a plane to New Zealand

763
01:13:43,435 --> 01:13:45,630
to begin a new life.

764
01:13:45,810 --> 01:13:49,730
You probably haven 't even noticed
I'd packed my bags.

765
01:13:49,894 --> 01:13:54,334
I have fallen in love
with my penfriend, Desmond,

766
01:13:54,519 --> 01:13:57,039
and I'm going to live
on his sheep farm.

767
01:13:59,645 --> 01:14:03,125
It's been hard to watch you become
a remnant of the person I once loved.

768
01:14:03,270 --> 01:14:06,070
Your research into m-m-mental illness
has been admirable

769
01:14:06,187 --> 01:14:11,347
but your i-idealistic pursuit to remedy it
has been misguided.

770
01:14:11,563 --> 01:14:14,600
Mary, you have to realise y-you are not
a magic beauty cream

771
01:14:14,813 --> 01:14:19,093
you can smooth on the world
to rid it of its wrinkles.

772
01:14:19,272 --> 01:14:21,072
I love you, Mary,

773
01:14:21,148 --> 01:14:24,308
but I love Desmond more.

774
01:14:24,440 --> 01:14:27,680
I hope one day your heart will heal
and we can be friends.

775
01:14:27,815 --> 01:14:30,807
Yours compassionately,
Damian.

776
01:14:53,818 --> 01:14:56,578
Aaaarghh!

777
