812
01:22:25,540 --> 01:22:29,300
When I received your book,
the emotions inside my brain

813
01:22:29,457 --> 01:22:34,326
felt like they were in a tumble dryer,
smashing into each other.

814
01:22:35,791 --> 01:22:40,031
The hurt felt like when I accidentally
stapled my lips together.

815
01:22:40,208 --> 01:22:41,800
Ow!

816
01:22:42,000 --> 01:22:47,320
The reason I forgive you
is because you are not perfect.

817
01:22:47,542 --> 01:22:51,382
You are imperfect, and so am l.

818
01:22:51,543 --> 01:22:54,423
All humans are imperfect,

819
01:22:54,543 --> 01:22:58,695
even the man outside my apartment
who litters.

820
01:22:58,960 --> 01:23:05,115
When I was young,
I wanted to be anybody but myself.

821
01:23:05,461 --> 01:23:09,261
Dr Bernard Hazelhof said
if I was on a desert island

822
01:23:09,420 --> 01:23:13,020
then I would have to get used
to my own company

823
01:23:13,171 --> 01:23:16,243
just me and the coconuts.

824
01:23:16,504 --> 01:23:22,739
He said I would have to accept myself,
my warts and all,

825
01:23:23,088 --> 01:23:25,928
and that we don't get to choose
our warts.

826
01:23:26,047 --> 01:23:29,517
They are a part of us
and we have to live with them.

827
01:23:31,548 --> 01:23:35,548
We can, however, choose our friends

828
01:23:35,715 --> 01:23:40,835
and I am glad I have chosen you.

829
01:23:41,049 --> 01:23:44,041
Dr Bernard Hazelhof also said

830
01:23:44,258 --> 01:23:48,578
that everyone's lives
are like a very long sidewalk.

831
01:23:48,758 --> 01:23:53,278
Some are well paved.
Others, like mine,

832
01:23:53,467 --> 01:23:58,827
have cracks, banana skins
and cigarette butts.

833
01:23:59,051 --> 01:24:05,729
Your sidewalk is like mine
but probably not as many cracks.

834
01:24:06,094 --> 01:24:09,882
Hopefully, one day
our sidewalks will meet

835
01:24:10,136 --> 01:24:13,606
and we can share
a can of condensed milk.

836
01:24:17,595 --> 01:24:23,591
You are my best friend.
You are my only friend.

837
01:24:23,929 --> 01:24:29,049
Your American penpal,
Max Jerry Horowitz.

838
01:24:30,597 --> 01:24:35,397
PS. I have recently found the perfect job
with a survey company.

839
01:24:35,597 --> 01:24:40,148
All I have to do is eat things
and tick boxes.

